✅ Java Code (You wrote)

public class Pattern {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
for(int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {   // rows
            for(int j = 1; j <= i; j++) { // columns
                System.out.print("* ");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}

✅ Output (Pattern)

* 
* * 
* * * 
* * * * 
* * * * * 
